<P><H1 align=center>VIEW SUB-QUOTES – CM075</H1>
<P></P>
<P>This screen is divided into two, the top half (Subquote Details and Costs) 
showing the quotes given – the loan amount, <A HREF="HELP_MortgageTerms.asp#LTV">LTV</A>, monthly cost, total net charges 
and which quote is active.</P>
<P>To reinstate a quote, highlight the line you wish to reactivate, and click 
‘reinstate’.</P>
<P>The bottom half (Loan Components) gives more detail about the mortgage loan 
itself – the product, rate type, interest rate, loan amount, Mortgage term, 
repayment type and monthly cost.</P>
<P>To show this detail, highlight the subquote in the top section, and the 
detail will be shown in the Loan Components section.</P>

